<span class="line"><span style="color:#89DDFF;">[</span><span style="color:#C792EA;">attribute</span><span style="color:#89DDFF;">|=</span><span style="color:#C3E88D;">value</span><span style="color:#89DDFF;">]</span><span style="color:#A6ACCD;">：选择attribute属性以value开头的元素</span></span>
